snippet.title: ELDEN RING – Rise, Tarnished | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Though shattered, it shall guide thee. Though fractured, it yet calls. Enact thy will. Become Lord. Seek the Elden Ring.

#ELDENRING launches February 25, 2022.
Pre-order ELDEN RING: https://bnent.eu/PreorderEldenRing
Join the ELDEN RING Discord: https://fcld.ly/eldenring_discord
